ifts)</p></li></ul></li><li __rdfaid=\"b1022d5c-02b6-4908-b9fb-f9a342c3d186\"><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">Equally divided living</p><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">For a minor who alternates between living with each of the parents according to the principle of equally divided living, you must also bring the following documents with you:</p><ul __rdfaid=\"975665a4-19af-45d8-b08b-190f31a7d303\"><li __rdfaid=\"6f7f3745-345c-4f5a-af21-c353fbdefe64\"><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">the mutual agreement of the parents,</p></li><li __rdfaid=\"8cf6adaa-a81b-4b10-b4e7-763991b71e22\"><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">the court decision,</p></li><li __rdfaid=\"b0e16457-3ea4-43c9-8a9e-ba6603812361\"><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">and the notarial deed.</p></li></ul></li><li __rdfaid=\"ae99bf38-ee54-4bca-9e0c-f8022165c3e5\"><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">or you can go to the Civil Affairs Office of your (new) municipality.</p></li></ul><p data-indentation-level=\"0\"><br>​Foreign nationality:<br></p><ul __rdfaid=\"a89efc0d-0be1-415a-a706-b1f185ee18af\"><li __rdfaid=\"9ed3e275-f3b9-4c4b-9215-a0144c2286b5\"><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">You can report the change of address via e-mail&nbsp;(vreemdelingen@aalst.be); please mention:​</p><ul __rdfaid=\"1623ed54-b88b-4982-97df-f68a0b6f6257\"><li __rdfaid=\"791004d6-45a1-440a-a7bb-d028c54c8e0d\"><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">your national registration number</p></li><li __rdfaid=\"870bb40b-44a5-4339-8d82-9a52f6b7f829\"><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">name and national registration number. of al&nbsp;the&nbsp;family members who are moving with you</p></li><li __rdfaid=\"bb481778-c755-465f-ba9e-a42eedc8927d\"><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">your new address</p></li><li __rdfaid=\"008861b8-6b24-4274-8131-6e9b2e34595f\"><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">whether the previous residents stay with you or move to another address</p></li><li __rdfaid=\"0ad4c3a5-b802-45d5-ac04-1c6ca21dbc19\"><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">your telephone of mobile number where the neighbourhood police officer can reach you</p></li><li __rdfaid=\"a027b5ce-0c99-4758-9657-542227edc33c\"><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">when you are at home (also mention when you work different shifts)</p></li></ul></li><li __rdfaid=\"b98a88d7-48e1-488c-9dc0-56e92562cd46\"><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">or you can go to the Civil Affairs Office of your (new) municipality; make&nbsp;an appointment online&nbsp;(choose&nbsp;\"Niet-Belg: Adreswijziging aanvragen\")</p></li></ul><p data-indentation-level=\"0\"></p><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">In order to report the change of address for the entire household, it is sufficient for one of the adult members of the household to do so.​</p><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">To be able to report the change of address, you need a valid identity document stating your national registration number.</p><p data-indentation-level=\"0\"><br>If an unemancipated minor leaves the residence of&nbsp;his&nbsp;parents for the first time in order to establish&nbsp;his&nbsp;main residence elsewhere,&nbsp;he&nbsp;must be accompanied by someone exercising parental authority.</p><p data-indentation-level=\"0\"></p><h3 data-indentation-level=\"0\" __rdfaid=\"f9f44a1c-6fde-4d35-a73c-e960ff7d4d0a\">Verification of domicile and update of identity documents:</h3><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">After reporting the change of address, a neighbourhood police officer or an authorised civil servant will check whether you actually have your main residence at the reported address. After this verification, you are registered at your new address and invited to the town hall to have your identity card updated. You will need your electronic identity card with the PIN for this. Make your appointment:&nbsp;</p><ul __rdfaid=\"f4339726-45bc-4f46-84c0-69d821d632ba\"><li __rdfaid=\"336a471f-a652-4167-bef5-e7ca886ca487\"><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">online;&nbsp;</p><ul __rdfaid=\"8f022c41-561c-4145-823e-e4b48241eddd\"><li __rdfaid=\"8c9188c6-4d03-466c-97cf-776b648f7bbf\"><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">choose&nbsp;\"Adreswijziging Belg: aanpassen identiteitskaart (1afspraak/gezin)\"&nbsp;if&nbsp;you&nbsp;are&nbsp;Belgian</p></li><li __rdfaid=\"4a9c6ce7-1349-4fad-a637-1473b7e9132e\"><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">​choose&nbsp;\"Niet-Belg: Adreswijziging kaart aanpassen\" if you&nbsp;have a&nbsp;foreign nationality</p></li></ul></li></ul><p data-indentation-level=\"0\"></p><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">Once your identity card has been updated, you can notify any other agencies of your change of address.</p><h3 data-indentation-level=\"0\" __rdfaid=\"e898575e-ac2b-49c1-bc20-5626342740ec\"><strong>Vehicle registration certificate</strong></h3><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">A change of address no longer needs to be entered on vehicle registration certificates. Vehicle registration certificates will only state the address that was valid at the time it was issued.</p>","nl-BE-x-generated-formal":"<p data-indentation-level=\"0\">U moet de adreswijziging melden aan de gemeente waar het nieuwe adres gelegen is.</p><h5 __rdfaid=\"890ec054-906d-4887-a7c4-39e6cd32a0dd\" data-indentation-level=\"0\">​Belgische nationaliteit, u verhuist binnen België:</h5><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">Doe uw aanvraag via email naar <a __rdfaid=\"3a6188e2-2a23-4a18-98cb-49035fbdc364\" href=\"javascript:location.href='mailto:'+String.fromCharCode(98,101,118,111,108,107,105,110,103,64,97,97,108,115,116,46,98,101)+'?%27\">bevolking@aalst.be</a>. of u kunt hiervoor langsgaan bij de dienst Burgerzaken van uw (nieuwe) gemeente.</p><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">Vermeldt of meebrengen</p><ul __rdfaid=\"428a2589-7191-4636-b6a8-b6f02820ee4d\"><li __rdfaid=\"5e48907d-127f-405e-8b6e-3b56d0dc6ff5\"><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">uw rijksregisternummer</p></li><li __rdfaid=\"90dae3ea-26e4-48b7-96a4-1bbcadce0e6d\"><p data-indentation-level=\"0\">naam of rijksregisternummer van alle gezinsleden die mee verhuizen</p></li><li __rdfaid=\"9459e